descript.abstract: This dataset represents the countires/islands neighboring the US. This dataset is from the updated version of the countries in ESRI Data and Maps CDs.
descript.purpose: This dataset is used to create the US Map Templates series.
descript.supplinf: This dataset is in Shapefile format, in geographic coordinates (latitude-longitude).
